title: Sesame Street
description: Join Big Bird, Oscar, Elmo, Bert, Cookie Monster, the Count and many other characters to learn the alphabet and to count with Count von Count, but most of all just have a good time.

videoEpisodes.title: Welcome to Sesame Hospital
videoEpisodes.description: Rosita, Abby, and Telly play hospital and pretend to be a doctor, nurse and x-ray technician. Chris pretends to be their patient and they help heal his funny bone.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 5 hours ago, available until 10:02am on 21 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: The Furry Four
videoEpisodes.description: Telly, Abby and Elmo want to pretend to be their favourite superheroes - The Furry Four.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 1 day ago, available until 10:01am on 20 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Earth Day
videoEpisodes.description: It's Earth Day on Sesame Street! Rudy learns to be kind to the earth after he sees what it would be like if everyone acted like him and threw their trash on the street.

videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 3 days ago, available until 10:03am on 18 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Julia's Haircut
videoEpisodes.description: Elmo, Abby and Alan play hair salon and pretend to be hair stylists to help Julia feel less scared about getting a haircut.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 4 days ago, available until 10:02am on 17 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Elmo the Engineer
videoEpisodes.description: Elmo and his dad become engineers as they design a 'toy putter awayer' to help Elmo put away his toys.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 5 days ago, available until 10:01am on 16 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Walking the Dog
videoEpisodes.description: Elmo wants to be a dog walker just like Dog Walker Grover. His friends help him practice by pretending to be different kinds of dogs.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 6 days ago, available until 10:00am on 15 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Elmo Goes to Chicken School
videoEpisodes.description: Elmo helps Professor Buck Awe teach a class of chickens using strategies he learned in preschool.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 1 week ago, available until 10:00am on 14 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Fishing X
videoEpisodes.description: Big Bird and Snuffy are the hosts of 'The Letter of the Day Show' on Sesame Street and learn all about how the letter X can come at the end of a word.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 1 week ago, available until 10:00am on 13 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.description: Rudy is pretending to be a space alien from another planet. When his space ship won't start, Abby and Elmo play mechanics. They figure out what the problem is and fix Rudy's space ship.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 1 week ago, available until 10:01am on 12 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Rudy Rides the Bus
videoEpisodes.description: Elmo and Rudy play bus driver and bus monitor, driving a homemade bus and helping their friends get around Sesame Street.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 1 week ago, available until 10:02am on 11 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Sesame Friendship
videoEpisodes.description: Big Bird builds a tall block castle and it accidentally gets knocked down. Big Bird thinks Snuffy did it without letting him explain. With Alan and Nina's help, they learn to stand up for themselves, listen and apologise.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 2 weeks ago, available until 10:02am on 10 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: The Big Pretend Band
videoEpisodes.description: Bert learns how to use his imagination and pretend play a saxophone so he can join his friends in their pretend band and play in a concert.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 2 weeks ago, available until 10:01am on 9 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Elmo's Happy Little Train
videoEpisodes.description: Elmo, Rosita, and Zoe play train and pretend to be the driver, conductor and passenger. They make up an adventure so Oscar can play too.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 2 weeks ago, available until 10:01am on 8 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Dinosaur in the Laundromat
videoEpisodes.description: There's a strange noise on Sesame Street that Rudy, Zoe, and Rosita keep hearing. To find out what's making this noise, they become scientists and observe, ask questions, and investigate.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 2 weeks ago, available until 10:01am on 7 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Astronaut Elmo
videoEpisodes.description: Rosita, Elmo and Abby pretend to be astronauts and use their imagination to go into space and with help from Chris, they figure out which 'space tool' to use to fix their ripped space ship.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 2 weeks ago, available until 10:01am on 6 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Bath Time For Blanky
videoEpisodes.description: Abby brings Rudy to the laundromat to wash his stinky blanky. Grover is the new laundromat attendant but he doesn't know how to use the machines. Luckily Chris shows them all how to use a washing machine and dryer.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 2 weeks ago, available until 10:01am on 5 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Play Time
videoEpisodes.description: Nina, Elmo, Abby, Big Bird and Chris put on a play about Little Miss Muffet. With the actors, narrator, costume designer and set designer jobs already planned out , Nina helps Big Bird find his job as playwright.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 2 weeks ago, available until 10:01am on 4 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: New Year's Eve Show
videoEpisodes.description: It's New Year's Eve on Sesame Street. Rosita and Telly try to help Elmo stay awake until the new year so he can celebrate with his friends.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 3 weeks ago, available until 10:01am on 3 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Math Magic
videoEpisodes.description: Max the Magician amazes Rosita, Big Bird and Elmo with his magical, mathematical tricks.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 3 weeks ago, available until 10:02am on 2 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Elmo's Factory
videoEpisodes.description: Elmo has a lot of anything holders to make so Chris helps Elmo put together his own factory. Elmo's friends work as a team and each take on a different job to help make the anything holders quicker.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 3 weeks ago, available until 10:02am on 1 Sep 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: So You Think Choreograph
videoEpisodes.description: Elmo and his friends are making a music video. They ask Zoe to be the choreographer, who comes up with the perfect dance and teaches everyone the moves.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 3 weeks ago, available until 10:00am on 31 Aug 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Hey! Sesame Street News
videoEpisodes.description: Cookie Monster is a journalist for Abby and Big Bird's newspaper 'Hey Sesame Street News!', He solves the mystery of Chris' missing belt buckle by asking the five W questions: who, what, where, when and why.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 3 weeks ago, available until 10:01am on 30 Aug 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Picture This
videoEpisodes.description: Alan gives Elmo, Rosita, and Abby his old cameras to play with and suggests that they can be photographers for the day. So Abby, Rosita, and Elmo go around Sesame Street taking pictures and learning how to use their cameras.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 3 weeks ago, available until 10:01am on 29 Aug 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: When You're a Vet
videoEpisodes.description: Abby and Elmo play veterinarians. By using their eyes, ears and hands, Abby and Elmo figure out what's wrong with their pretend patients and help them feel better.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 3 weeks ago, available until 10:01am on 28 Aug 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Episode 9
videoEpisodes.description: Abby and Zoe are very excited for Leela to read them a story, but Leela keeps texting on her phone. Abby and Zoe become frustrated, so they decide to hide her phone, until she reads the story.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 4 weeks ago, available until 10:00am on 27 Aug 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Episode 8
videoEpisodes.description: Chris begins reading a story about a Mexican but Rosita stops him, explaining that there is so much more to being Mexican than siestas, sombreros, and burros. She wishes that there was a book that showed how she really lived.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 4 weeks ago, available until 10:00am on 26 Aug 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Episode 7
videoEpisodes.description: Alan is outside painting a picture of a bowl of fruit. Cookie Monster walks by and tries to eat the fruit, but thinks the bowl of fruit is there to eat. Alan stops him and explains that he is painting a picture of the fruit.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 4 weeks ago, available until 9:59am on 25 Aug 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Episode 6
videoEpisodes.description: Telly and Rosita decide to become robots to help Chris at Hooper's store. They call themselves the Help-O-Bots. At first they are a really big help but then they start going faster and end up making more of a mess for Chris.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 4 weeks ago, available until 10:00am on 24 Aug 2019.

videoEpisodes.title: Episode 5
videoEpisodes.description: There's a big "Simon Says" competition on Sesame Street, and players from all over have come to see who is the best at "Simon Says!" Elmo was supposed to be the player for Sesame Street, but he is too young to play.
videoEpisodes.availability: This episode was published 4 weeks ago, available until 10:00am on 23 Aug 2019.
